overview: What sets us apart from other dentists in Collierville is our dedication to quality service. For patients who need more than basic dental care, our office offers restorative dentistry treatment, like inlays, onlays and crowns. We also offer partial and full dentures for people with missing tooth/teeth. With our restorative services, we aim to repair damaged and/or decayed teeth. Dr. Breazeal and his team will ensure that your teeth are restored to their proper look and function. This is why Dr. Breazal is one of the best dentists Collierville has to offer.
